            <h3>About the project</h3> 
            <p>
                Users can search for information about their favorite movies. The application fetches data
                in real-time from the OMDb API and displays it in a user-friendly format. You can learn how
                to use it here <a href="https://www.omdbapi.com/">Open Movie Api</a>.
            </p>
            <h5>Tech Stack used on this project</h5>
            <p>
                For this project, I utilized the <strong>Blazor framework</strong>, a powerful web
