            </p>
            <h5>Clean and Minimalist UI</h5>
            <p>
                I believe in the power of simplicity. The user interface is designed to be clean and intuitive, 
                ensuring that visitors can easily navigate and find the information they're looking for.
            </p>
            <h5>How it works?</h5>
            <p>
                The usage of this software is very simple, you just right the name of the movie on the search section,
                then you press the search button and if the movie exist, it will show you the information related to
                the movie, and also will store the previous results of the search on the page.
